00:20:26.830 --> 00:20:29.400
it's important to know
and check the effects

00:20:29.400 --> 00:20:32.530
on the surrounding environment.

00:20:34.600 --> 00:20:35.900
In most countries,

00:20:35.900 --> 00:20:37.870
governments have laws
about what's allowed

00:20:37.870 --> 00:20:40.070
to go into the air, the water,

00:20:40.070 --> 00:20:43.630
and the food
that people are exposed to.

00:20:43.630 --> 00:20:46.730
Scientists can test
for the presence of mutagens

00:20:46.730 --> 00:20:51.300
in our environment, food,
or in chemicals we use.

00:20:51.300 --> 00:20:53.370
The Ames test can be used
to find out

00:20:53.370 --> 00:20:56.100
whether a chemical is mutagenic.

00:20:56.100 --> 00:20:58.530
Scientists can also test
for the presence

00:20:58.530 --> 00:21:01.500
of specific mutagens like lead.

00:21:07.800 --> 00:21:09.900
DNA is a complex molecule.

00:21:09.900 --> 00:21:11.730
It's vital to the structure
and health

00:21:11.730 --> 00:21:15.930
of every cell in our body.

00:21:15.930 --> 00:21:19.000
Mutagens are things
that can change DNA,

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:21.430
and when the bases of our DNA
are changed,

00:21:21.430 --> 00:21:23.800
they can no longer code
for the same protein,

00:21:23.800 --> 00:21:28.200
and this can have a drastic
effect on the cell's function.

00:21:28.200 --> 00:21:31.700
Luckily, our DNA
usually repairs itself,

00:21:31.700 --> 00:21:35.230
and a lot of changes
don't have any effect.

00:21:35.230 --> 00:21:37.070
In some of the worst cases,

00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:41.470
mutations can lead
to genetic diseases or cancer.

00:21:45.370 --> 00:21:48.500
Today scientists have developed
a range of tests

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:50.430
to find out more about mutagens

00:21:50.430 --> 00:21:53.430
and to test the chemicals
that we come into contact with.

00:21:53.430 --> 00:21:56.930
In the future, we'll know
even more about mutations

00:21:56.930 --> 00:22:00.400
and we'll find even better ways
to repair damaged DNA

